title: Madhya Pradesh Tunnel Caves In, 7 Labourers Rescued, 2 Still Trapped - NDTV
content: Madhya Pradesh Tunnel Caves In, 7 Labourers Rescued, 2 Still Trapped  NDTVView Full coverage on Google News
description: Nine labourers were trapped after an under-construction tunnel of the Bargi canal project caved in at Sleemanabad in Katni district of Madhya Pradesh. Relief operations are on and seven of the nine labourers have been rescued.
